Good....nhung can luu y xai lau ben  1.ko nen soc khoai tay ru ray cam ma dung dua tron deu....  2.luon luon cho ir nhat 1 muong dau caphe....se ruyet  3.khoai tay nen chia thoi gian lam 2 lan..lan 1=15&#039;..la ra dung dua dao tron deu roi cho vao  lan 2=10&#039; hay 15&#039; tuy muon gion hay hoi gion.....  4.sau khi lam xong khong beb rua lien ma de nguoi sau do hay sua bang tam bot.  chuc ban xai ben lau....